data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! SELLER OFFERING $10K CLOSING CREDIT! This Mid-Century Modern walkout ranch is located on a corner lot in the heart of Lincoln. Admire the sleek design, expansive windows, and harmonious integration with nature. The main floor of this home boasts a large living room with mid-century modern features, 3 bedrooms, first-floor laundry, kitchen with an adjoining dining space. The large master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom and plenty of closet space.  The additional bedrooms are equally well-appointed and versatile. The basement has a second kitchen, family room, large bedroom with full ensuite bathroom, and plenty of storage. The yard is landscaped and well-maintained with a back patio for entertaining. Enjoy being centrally located with easy access to local parks, shopping, & dining. Its location is perfect for leisurely walks and bike rides.
